        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-08-17T17:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1949-08-17T17:00:00-05:00" n="972" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d972">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.6363/8–249: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Consul at Tsingtao</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hawthorne</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-08-17T18:00:00-04:00">August 17, 1949—6 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>241. Request info source Avigas shipped Peiping account Communist urtel 399
                    August 2. Caltex office here reports company’s Tsingtao Avigas stocks under 100
                    bbls.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
